b'Aikatsu Planet!': b'The story revolves around "Aikatsu Planet," a state-of-the-art virtual world where anyone can assume the role of an avatar and becoming a most popular virtual idol. Mao Otoha, an ordinary first-year student at the private academy Seirei High School, becomes a top idol avatar Hana when Hana\'s previous alter ego Meisa Hinata suddenly disappeared. However, Mao\'s new role as the avatar Hana is a secret to everyone else.\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)'
